sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Utilizator
    participant FE as Frontend - pagina Meciuri
    participant WS as winProbabilityService
    participant BE as Backend FastAPI
    participant AF as API-Football
    participant MP as Mapper
    participant PS as PredictionService - LightGBM
    participant DB as Stocare JSON

    U->>FE: Selecteaza un meci
    FE->>WS: submitPredictionByFixtureId(fixtureId)
    WS->>BE: POST /predict/by-fixture-id { fixture_id } + JWT
    BE->>BE: Verifica token JWT

    Note over BE,AF: Doua apeluri suplimentare catre API-Football
    BE->>AF: GET /fixtures/statistics?fixture=ID
    AF-->>BE: Statistici (suturi, xG, pase, posesie)
    BE->>AF: GET /fixtures/events?fixture=ID
    AF-->>BE: Evenimente (goluri, cartonase)

    BE->>MP: map_api_football_to_match_input(...)
    MP-->>BE: MatchInput

    BE->>PS: predict(MatchInput)
    PS->>PS: Construieste vectorul de 33 features
    PS->>PS: LightGBM predict_proba + analiza timeline (momentum, momente decisive)
    PS->>DB: Salveaza predictia (fisier JSON per utilizator)
    PS-->>BE: Probabilitati + momente decisive

    BE-->>WS: PredictionResponse
    WS-->>FE: Date predictie
    FE-->>U: Afiseaza probabilitatile, graficul si momentele cheie
